728349f-a.title: Richmond: Arden Avenue - Whalley Avenue
728349f-a.text:
1167 Arden Ave., north side, between Whalley Ave. and Van
Brunt Street, showing the Gaptain James Mclaughlin residence, called
the ''Rosebud Cottage.'' The view is eastward from the property.
May 17, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
